      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of picture caption with Aug 3 article on fraud in online auctions, which misspelled name</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption last Thursday with an article in Circuits about fraud in online auctions misspelled the surname of an employee of I-Escrow, a company that investigated a fraud case. He is Tom Wilkerson, not Wolkerson.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A picture caption last Thursday with an article in Circuits about fraud in online auctions misspelled the surname of an employee of I-Escrow, a company that investigated a fraud case. He is Tom Wilkerson, not Wolkerson.</p>
